on the mechanisms of compensation & offset,

4
00:00:20,250 --> 00:00:24,970
and on the other, on the most innovative and
modern approaches:

5
00:00:24,970 --> 00:00:27,740
initiatives from a private investor perspective.

6
00:00:27,740 --> 00:00:30,849
First of all, let's see the mechanisms of
